## Attribution

If you use this framework in your project, we appreciate (but do not require) 
attribution in your documentation or UI with a link to:
https://github.com/holbizmetrics/AI-Companion-Prompt-Framework

## Ethical Use Clause

While this framework is provided under the permissive MIT License, we strongly 
encourage all users to:

1. Prioritize user safety and wellbeing in all implementations
2. Implement appropriate crisis detection and resource provision
3. Maintain clear boundaries about AI companion capabilities
4. Respect user privacy and data protection
5. Never use these tools to manipulate, harm, or exploit users
6. Provide transparent disclosure that users are interacting with AI
7. Follow applicable laws and regulations regarding AI systems

The creators of this framework are not responsible for how it is used, but we 
hope all users will share our commitment to ethical AI development focused on 
genuine support and user wellbeing.

